{"tid":2193707,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"跨國議會聯盟撐港人爭選舉權","createTime":"2020-09-08T04:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T04:53:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"53a93e4ac91b038ceb77bfa2431177d322ff6f40","tid":2193707,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/7MYWKYQWDBGNTOIOKVNNHN4KXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2F7MYWKYQWDBGNTOIOKVNNHN4KXQ%2F&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqPdnC8dk%2FAL47v0imjzWEG4%3D&h=0b95279e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2F7MYWKYQWDBGNTOIOKVNNHN4KXQ%2F&h=ddc93924\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/7MYWKYQWDBGNTOIOKVNNHN4KXQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n跨國議會聯盟撐港人爭選舉權<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】網民前日發起在九龍區遊行，要求恢復舉行立法會選舉。警方拘捕約300人並以武力鎮壓市民，包括向手無寸鐵市民發射胡椒球彈。由十多國國會議員組成的「對華政策跨國議會聯盟」（Inter-Parliamentary Alliance on China，IPAC）聲援示威者訴求，呼籲國際社會適當回應。<br />\n<br />\nIPAC在Twitter表示，前日原本是香港舉行立法會選舉的日子，但港人選舉權利被剝奪，反對派陣營候選人更被取消資格，許多社運人士及新聞工作者被捕。IPAC呼籲國際社會作出適當回應。IPAC今年7月成立，目前有英美澳加等17個國家國會及歐洲議會議員共150名成員，宗旨是團結各國有志一同的國會議員深層合作，制訂積極應對中國的戰略。<br />\n<br />\n前日的九龍區遊行受到國際傳媒關注，英國《衞報》指這次遊行是港區國安法在7月1日實施以來，本港最大型的街頭示威。美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）指去年6月反送中示威以來，香港政局一直動盪，危機未有消退迹象，只是武漢肺炎疫情殺到和需要保持社交距離，令公眾失去集會的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/_PU0-tta5H0FMdiJy-5ISO2hIwg=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5TPUFL7STZH6VN5D4BGE5H6ZRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F_PU0-tta5H0FMdiJy-5ISO2hIwg%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5TPUFL7STZH6VN5D4BGE5H6ZRE.jpg&h=6604d72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■周日九龍區遊行有市民戴上寫有「還我選舉權」的紙箱，抗議政府押後立法會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《紐時》：警扼殺示威<br />\n<br />\n美國《華盛頓郵報》報道指，前日選民應該選擇新立法會議員，示威者返回香港街頭挑戰政府在武漢肺炎疫情下，將選舉..............................<br />\n<br />\n美國《華爾街日報》指，前日人群眾多且戴了口罩，很難確定誰在叫口號、誰在購物。惟防暴警察在旺角衝向人群捉拿懷疑示威者，......................."},{"pid":"217886a3c634c84a2985f6d90d4eee710b9fe170","tid":2193707,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"IPAC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60037d5b41a9004f17eed8aceac4923710e86ba2","tid":2193707,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T04:53:46.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}